      "content": "The data suggests that the net result of \"woke culture\" has been a shift towards greater accountability and consequences formisogynistic and racist behavior. Many institutions have implemented policies and procedures to address issues of bias and harassment, and high-profile cases of cancel culture have led to more severe repercussions for offenders. Conversely, a heightened sense of caution has indeed driven some people to self-censor, but this is likely a necessary cost to ensure that marginalized groups feel heard and protected.",
